                            Beamlines at the ALS

                      "" Clickable ALS Beamline Diagram

     Beamline data is available through the links below, and individual
     beamline data sheets are available in Portable Document Format
     (PDF). To view the PDF documents, you will need Adobe Acrobat
     Reader. See Adobe's Acrobat Reader Web page to download this free
     software. Tools to make PDFs more accessible to people with visual
     disabilities are available at access.adobe.com.



